&lt;title&gt;Back from FOSDEM&lt;/title&gt;
&lt;link&gt;<a href="http://tapoueh.org/blog/2011/02/07-back-from-fosdem.html">http://tapoueh.org/blog/2011/02/07-back-from-fosdem.html</a>&lt;/link&gt;
&lt;description&gt;&lt;![CDATA[h1&gt;Back from FOSDEM&lt;/h1&gt;
