<blockquote>
<p class="quoted">&lt;author&gt;<a href="mailto:dim@tapoueh.org">dim@tapoueh.org</a> (Dimitri Fontaine)&lt;/author&gt;
&lt;pubDate&gt;Tue, 31 Aug 2010 14:15:00 +0200&lt;/pubDate&gt;
&lt;guid isPermaLink=&quot;true&quot;&gt;<a href="http://tapoueh.org/blog/2010/08/31-want-to-share-your-recipes.html">http://tapoueh.org/blog/2010/08/31-want-to-share-your-recipes.html</a>&lt;/guid&gt;
