any mouse usage in the production of this diagram.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre class=&quot;src&quot;&gt;
convert .../pg_staging/bird-view.png -crop &lt;span style=&quot;color: #ad7fa8; font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;'!550'&lt;/span&gt; bird-view.png
