&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;../../../tags/emacs.html&quot;&gt;Emacs&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


</div>

<p>]]&gt;&lt;/description&gt;
<blockquote>
<p class="quoted">&lt;author&gt;<a href="mailto:dim@tapoueh.org">dim@tapoueh.org</a> (Dimitri Fontaine)&lt;/author&gt;
&lt;pubDate&gt;Thu, 24 Sep 2009 18:08:00 +0200&lt;/pubDate&gt;
&lt;guid isPermaLink=&quot;true&quot;&gt;<a href="http://tapoueh.org/blog/2009/09/24-emacs-is-twinkling-here.html">http://tapoueh.org/blog/2009/09/24-emacs-is-twinkling-here.html</a>&lt;/guid&gt;
