<blockquote>
<p class="quoted">&lt;author&gt;<a href="mailto:dim@tapoueh.org">dim@tapoueh.org</a> (Dimitri Fontaine)&lt;/author&gt;
&lt;pubDate&gt;Wed, 27 May 2009 14:30:00 +0200&lt;/pubDate&gt;
&lt;guid isPermaLink=&quot;true&quot;&gt;<a href="http://tapoueh.org/blog/2009/05/27-pgcon-2009.html">http://tapoueh.org/blog/2009/05/27-pgcon-2009.html</a>&lt;/guid&gt;
