<blockquote>
<p class="quoted">&lt;author&gt;<a href="mailto:dim@tapoueh.org">dim@tapoueh.org</a> (Dimitri Fontaine)&lt;/author&gt;
&lt;pubDate&gt;Wed, 28 Jan 2009 00:00:00 +0100&lt;/pubDate&gt;
&lt;guid isPermaLink=&quot;true&quot;&gt;<a href="http://tapoueh.org/blog/2009/01/28-controling-hot-usage-in-83.html">http://tapoueh.org/blog/2009/01/28-controling-hot-usage-in-83.html</a>&lt;/guid&gt;
